	<h1 class="title">《一吻定情》看多少遍都不腻，泰剧版还是满满少女心</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/117425/small/117425.?1433669313" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王珊珊 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-29 19:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16784/medium/16784.jpg?1446100453" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="16784" data-title="《《一吻定情》看多少遍都不腻，泰剧版还是满满少女心》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16784/medium/16784.jpg?1446100453" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16784.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
